'''杰夫瑞·卡普兰'''（{{lang-en|Jeffrey Kaplan}}），是原[[暴雪娱乐|暴雪娱乐]]的游戏设计师，于2002年加入暴雪，于2021年离职。

==早期生活==
卡普兰出生于[[美国|美国]][[新泽西州|新泽西州]]，在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[拉肯亚达─弗林楚奇|拉肯亚达─弗林楚奇]]长大。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.latimes.com/socal/burbank-leader/news/tn-blr-me-burbank-arena-esports-20180111-story.html | title = Burbank's Blizzard Arena aims to take esports to the next level | first = Jeff | last = Landa | date = 2018-01-11 | access-date = 2018-01-12 | work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | archive-date = 2018-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180112152354/http://www.latimes.com/socal/burbank-leader/news/tn-blr-me-burbank-arena-esports-20180111-story.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>卡普兰在上学期间一直是一名狂热的游戏玩家，尤其受到[[Infocom|Infocom]]的影响。由于缺乏编程技能，他从未想在游戏行业获得工作。<ref name="gi part1"/>他最初攻读电影学位，在[[南加州大学|南加州大学]]获得创意写作学位。他在环球影业担任写作实习生后，决定去纽约大学获得创意写作研究生学位。<ref name="gi part1">{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/03/30/from-guild-leader-to-game-director-pt-1-landing-a-job-at-blizzard.aspx | title = From Guild Leader to Game Director Part 1: Landing A Job At Blizzard | first = Daniel | last = Tack | date = 2016-03-30 | access-date = 2017-05-27 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211117054022/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/03/30/from-guild-leader-to-game-director-pt-1-landing-a-job-at-blizzard.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>在此之后，他在父亲的招聘公司工作，并一边进行写作，试图让自己的作品发表，但过了几年来，他都没有成功发表任何一部作品，其中最夸张的一年收到172封拒绝信。到了2000年，他决定放弃写作，把时间花在游戏上。<ref name="gi part1"/><ref name="9things"/>

==职业生涯==
卡普兰玩游戏《无尽的任务》，加入了“钢铁之遗”公会，因成就和在公会网站上发表的对游戏的评论而出名。<ref name="gi part1"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://legacyofsteel.net/#/members|title=Legacy of Steel|website=legacyofsteel.net|access-date=2017-05-22|archive-date=2021-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210729003816/https://legacyofsteel.net/#/members|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于他经常讨论地图制作，引起了公会会长[[罗布·帕尔多|罗布·帕尔多]]（《[[魔兽争霸3|魔兽争霸3]]》首席设计师）的注意。 2001年左右，帕尔多邀请卡普兰参观暴雪在洛杉矶的办公室，在此期间他被介绍给其他几位暴雪的公会成员，他们向他展示一款未公布的[[大型多人在线游戏|大型多人在线游戏]]项目（即《魔兽世界 》）<ref name="gi part1"/>。在接下来的几个月里，他参与了几次类似的会议。<ref name="9things"/>在《魔兽世界》公布后，帕尔多建议卡普兰向暴雪申请一份魔兽世界任务设计师的工作，卡普兰意识到职位是为他量身定制的，最初参观暴雪实际是非正式的面试。2002年，卡普兰加入暴雪。<ref name="gi part1"/>

卡普兰在暴雪最初的工作是在《[[魔兽争霸III：混乱之治|魔兽争霸III：混乱之治]]》发布前几周保证其质量，游戏发售后，他以任务设计师的身份加入了魔兽世界团队。卡普兰的工作是负责《魔兽世界》的环境元素，包括任务设计和地下城、突袭战的整体美感。<Ref name="gi w3">
{{Cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/games/world_of_warcraft_cataclysm/b/pc/archive/2009/12/02/blizzard-s-jeff-kaplan-on-warcraft-s-past-and-future.aspx | title = Blizzard's Jeff Kaplan on Warcraft's Past And Future | first = Phil | last = Kollar | date = 2009-12-02 | access-date = 2017-05-24 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-date = 2021-01-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210122222229/https://www.gameinformer.com/games/world_of_warcraft_cataclysm/b/pc/archive/2009/12/02/blizzard-s-jeff-kaplan-on-warcraft-s-past-and-future.aspx | dead-url = no }}
</ref>最终，卡普兰成为魔兽世界的游戏总监。<ref name="engadget titan">{{Cite web | url = https://www.engadget.com/2009/02/12/jeff-kaplan-leaving-world-of-warcraft/ | title = Jeff Kaplan leaving World of Warcraft | first = Elizabeth | last = Harper | date = 2009-02-12 | access-date = 2017-05-24 | work = [[Engadget|Engadget]] | archive-date = 2018-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181006121928/https://www.engadget.com/2009/02/12/jeff-kaplan-leaving-world-of-warcraft/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2009年2月，卡普兰宣布他辞去魔兽世界总监一职，参与一个未经公布的大型多人在线游项目（即《泰坦》）。卡普兰选择加入这个新项目，希望能够制造与魔兽世界类似的成功，但开发周期漫长且艰难，《泰坦》于2014年9月正式宣布取消开发。<ref name="Titancancelled">{{cite web | url = http://www.polygon.com/2014/9/23/6833953/blizzard-cancels-titan-next-gen-mmo-pc | title = Blizzard cancels its next-gen MMO Titan after seven years | last = Kollar | first = Philip | publisher = [[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] | date = 2014-09-23 | access-date = 2021-07-16 | archive-date = 2014-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140923203528/http://www.polygon.com/2014/9/23/6833953/blizzard-cancels-titan-next-gen-mmo-pc | dead-url = no }}</ref>

在泰坦正式宣布取消之前，游戏开发已于2013年初中止。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.seattletimes.com/business/technology/game-designer-jeffrey-kaplan-failed-big-but-hes-back-on-top/ | title = Game designer Jeffrey Kaplan failed big, but he's back on top | first = Parish | last = Dave | date = 2016-01-10 | access-date = 2017-05-24 | work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | archive-date = 2018-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180809030247/https://www.seattletimes.com/business/technology/game-designer-jeffrey-kaplan-failed-big-but-hes-back-on-top/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>除了40名泰坦开发成员外，其他人被分配到其他项目，管理层要求在几周内提出新的方案，否则开发团队会被解散。卡普兰和[[克里斯·梅森|克里斯·梅森]]带领团队，在借鉴泰坦的一些游戏玩法和创意元素后，开发一款团队射击游戏，即后来的《守望先锋》。项目获得暴雪批准后，卡普兰成为游戏的首席总监，梅森担任创意总监。<ref name="9things">{{cite web|quote=He was a failed poet who became the director of one of the most popular games in the world|url=http://www.glixel.com/interviews/9-things-you-didnt-know-about-blizzards-jeff-kaplan-w455480|title=9 Things You Didn't Know About 'Overwatch' Director Jeff Kaplan|first=Heather|last=Newman|work=Glixel|date=2016-12-12|access-date=2016-12-14|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707042933/http://www.glixel.com/interviews/9-things-you-didnt-know-about-blizzards-jeff-kaplan-w455480|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="eurogamer kaplan ama">{{Cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-03-14-blizzards-jeff-kaplan-traces-line-from-project-titan-to-overwatch | title = Blizzard's Jeff Kaplan traces line from Project Titan to Overwatch | first = Wesley | last = Yin-Poole | date = 2017-03-14 | access-date = 2017-03-14 | work = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-date = 2017-03-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170315001401/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-03-14-blizzards-jeff-kaplan-traces-line-from-project-titan-to-overwatch | dead-url = no }}</ref>《守望先锋》在商业上获得巨大成功，第一年的收入就超过10 亿美元，并在全球吸引了超过3500万玩家。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-04-28-overwatch-now-has-30m-players | title = Overwatch now has 30m players | date = 2017-04-28 | access-date = 017-04-28 | work = [[GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]] | archive-date = 2018-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180810144113/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-04-28-overwatch-now-has-30m-players | dead-url = no }}</ref>卡普兰受到《[[炉石传说|炉石传说]]》首席总监本·布罗德的启发，经常公开露面与《守望先锋》的粉丝互动，定期在《守望先锋》论坛上发帖，并制作了多个视频公开《守望先锋》的发展和后续更新。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web | url = http://www.glixel.com/news/overwatch-director-jeff-kaplan-is-freaked-out-by-his-fame-w483939 | title = 'Overwatch' Director Jeff Kaplan is Famous and It Freaks Him Out | first = Luke | last = Winkie | date = 2017-05-24 | access-date = 2017-05-24 | work = [[Glixel|Glixel]] | archive-date = 2017-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170703163219/http://www.glixel.com/news/overwatch-director-jeff-kaplan-is-freaked-out-by-his-fame-w483939 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2021年4月20日，暴雪宣布卡普兰离开公司，由亚伦凯勒接任卡普兰的位置。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.polygon.com/22394111/overwatch-jeff-kaplan-quits-blizzard-aaron-keller | title = Overwatch game director Jeff Kaplan leaves Blizzard | first = Michael | last = McWhertor | date = 2021-04-20 | accessdate = 2021-04-20 | work = [[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] | archive-date = 2021-04-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210420174742/https://www.polygon.com/22394111/overwatch-jeff-kaplan-quits-blizzard-aaron-keller | dead-url = no }}</ref>

